{"ID":"20260424101859-6aak6xd","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-6aak6xd","title":"01_前置基础","type":"doc","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101859-e58r8oj","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-e58r8oj","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"01 前置基础"}]},{"ID":"20260424101859-ftycelc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-ftycelc","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"后面的 NPU 架构、数据流、编译器、runtime 看起来像不同层的问题，实际上都绕不开同一组前提："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"工作负载的张量形状"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​、"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"乘加与归约"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​、"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"数据搬运成本"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​、"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"并行组织方式"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​、"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"性能/能效指标"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​。这些前提如果没稳住，后面看到 PE、MAC、dataflow、tile、kernel 时就只是在记名词。"}]},{"ID":"20260424101859-kky7mhg","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-kky7mhg","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1. 从神经网络到硬件，先做一次最短翻译"}]},{"ID":"20260424101859-s84emke","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-s84emke","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"神经网络对硬件并不神秘。把模型压扁以后，硬件真正面对的是三件事："}]},{"ID":"20260424101859-w9qydj5","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-w9qydj5","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101859-b8lp5rv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-b8lp5rv","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101859-qd7sl4n","Type":"NodeParagra